  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While engaged in combat with a creature whom the Land of Pipes or the Rain Village considers a hostile entity, you begin to experience flash backs of the death and desolation your village/country has experienced and you vow to NEVER allow that to happen again. <br />When rolling initiative, select one hostile creature. <br />That creature becomes Rain marked. <br />You will exclusively target and attack a Rain marked creature until they are dead. <br />Additionally, while in the Land of Pipes, you cannot lose concentration on jutsu you cast as a result of damage on being incapacitated.</p>",
